OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly dry and bright with some
OL,6,Fsunshine at times, and fairly light
OL,7,Fwinds. Cloud increasing across
OL,8,FShetland during the afternoon. Winds
OL,9,Fwill be mainly light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry start to the evening
OL,12,Fthen cloud thickening to bring some
OL,13,Foutbreaks of mainly light rain.
OL,14,FPerhaps some patchy haar. Light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FShetland cloudy with
OL,17,Foutbreaks of rain in the morning
OL,18,Fbecoming drier in the afternoon.
OL,19,FOrkney mostly dry but cloudy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
